    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "060\nAlong the way of TWA ...\nTAJ MAHAL\nIndia\nCreated by the\nShah Jahan in 1645\nas a memorial\nto his wife,\nthe exquisite white\nmarble Taj Mahal\nis located at Agra,\nnear the city of Delhi.\nTWA\nTRANS WORLD AIRLINES\nU. S. A. • EUROPE\nAFRICA • ASIA",
      "Erigé par le Shah Jahan en 1645 pour per\npétuer la mémoire de son épouse, le Taj\nMahal, joyau de marbre blanc, se trouve a Agra, pres de la ville\nde Delhi, Indes, un\ndes\npays desservis par la TWA.\nTWA\nPOST CARD\nUSE\nAIR\nMAIL\n2002.113. 463"
